{"tid":995259,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教師認兩度盜運動袋　待心理及精神報告候判","createTime":"2019-01-25T09:58:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T12:53:56.000Z","uid":2845,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"01592f68911e0010d8f528cc0df24768687ebbba","tid":995259,"uid":2845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T09:58:07.000Z","msg":"一名教師被指於去年12月兩度於跑馬地運動場更衣室內偷走兩個運動袋，被告<span style=\"color: red;\">陳建國</span>(33歲)今日(25日)承認兩項盜竊罪，准保釋至4月2日等候感化、社服令、心理及精神報告判刑。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，被告事發時在運動場男更衣室順手牽羊盜去兩個運動袋，內有手提電話及銀包等財物。被告今透過律師求情稱他已認罪後悔，屬初犯，事後主動向學校辭去工作了11年的教職，事發時因精神壓力犯案，現已向心理及精神科求診，希望給予機會輕判。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190125/mobile/bkn-20190125142725483-0125_00822_001.html\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190125%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190125142725483-0125_00822_001.html&h=70eff730&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人識佢 印象中好老師黎"},{"pid":"f901e7eb500ec99d78550fe40ea533692773e6fc","tid":995259,"uid":2845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T09:58:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190125/mobile/bkn-20190125142725483-0125_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190125%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190125142725483-0125_00822_001.html&d=Ev%2FgGGd3hbiNhm%2BUCJXp8DACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=b113ea47\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190125/mobile/bkn-20190125142725483-0125_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f02022a90a2d47a32d08b16988518c220922ad4a","tid":995259,"uid":197584,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T10:02:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff539e5f1b80968620f8b78ecad94d64da5f222","tid":995259,"uid":3501